Key Technical Challenges
	1.	World consistency

Maintaining stable objects across generative updates.
	2.	Latency

Real-time responsiveness required for conversational control.
	3.	Scene memory

The system must track persistent state across the simulation timeline.
	4.	Generation cost

High compute demands for dynamic world creation.

